Zumba Fitness, LLC is a Florida limited liability company with its principal place of business located at 800 Silks Run, Suite 2310, Hallandale, Florida USA 33009 (“Zumba”, “us,” “we” or “our”). If you are a resident in the European Economic Area ("EEA"), Switzerland, or the United Kingdom, Zumba Fitness, LLC is the responsible party or data controller with respect to Personal Data (defined below) we collect. If you have any questions or concerns at any time, please do not hesitate to contact us at the address above or by contacting us at
privacy@zumba.com
