Operating system;
Date and time of visit;
Pages visited and duration of visit;
Interactions with website elements (e.g., clicks, scrolls, and form inputs).
Purpose of Using FullStory:
The data collected helps us understand how users interact with our Sites, identify areas for improvement, and enhance the overall user experience. FullStory does not collect sensitive information, such as credit card details or passwords.
Opt-Out Option:
