Contract:
It is necessary to process Personal Data to perform a contract with you or because you have requested we do something before creating a contract with you that requires we process Personal Data. For example, we rely on Contract when we process your name, email address, and payment detail when you register for a Zumba® or Strong Nation® Instructor Training Course or obtain your Instructor License.
Legitimate Interest:
There is a commercial or business interest that is important to us or others which we've balanced against your privacy rights. For example, we rely on Legitimate Interest to process Personal Data to improve our products and services.
Consent:
We have asked for your permission to use Personal Data. For example, we obtain your Consent to process geolocation information.
Legal Obligation:
It is necessary to use Personal Data so that we can fulfil our legal and regulatory obligations. For example, our Legal Obligations may require us to maintain certain records to fulfil recordkeeping obligations.
